headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: Nagasaki Outlaw
content: Stop by The Diamond Casino & Resort to give the Lucky Wheel a spin to walk away with GTA$, RP, clothes, snacks, plus all sorts of mystery prizes. This week on the podium is the Nagasaki Outlaw, a buggy explicitly engineered to squeeze every drop of adrenaline out of its drivers.
